@startuml
title Identity Propagation
actor User
participant Orchestrator
participant Security
participant Gateway
participant Executor
participant Tool
participant Resource
User -> Orchestrator: authenticated request
Orchestrator -> Security: policy check
Security --> Orchestrator: execution context
Orchestrator -> Gateway: delegated request
Gateway -> Security: token exchange
Security --> Gateway: scoped token
Gateway -> Executor: delegated identity
Executor -> Tool: tool-scoped invocation
Tool -> Resource: resource access
Resource --> Tool: data/result
Tool --> Executor: normalized output
@enduml
